Robert H. Ramsey et al., Appellants, v. May U. Conoley, Appellees. An Appeal from a Decree of the Circuit Court within and for the County of Orange. Arthur F. Odlin, for Appellants; Rohmson & Bridges and DiokAnson & Diekmson, for Appellees.
